1. Clone git tree
git clone ssh://hr024065@gerrit-lvn-07.lvn.broadcom.net:29422/DCSG_PCIE/PCI4_ARM_FW
cd PCI4_ARM_FW
scp -p -P 29422 hr024065@gerrit-lvn-07.lvn.broadcom.net:hooks/commit-msg .git/hooks/

2. Make sure your tree is upto date
git pull

3. All changes need a JIRA ticket. commit logs should be of the following form
   Make the comments descriptive.
    [JIRA PEXSW-248]
    
    <your comment in multiple lines. don't make the lines too long>

4. Create a local branch for every new changeset 
git branch <branchname>
git checkout <branchname>

5. Make your changes and commit
git status --- will tell you what to do

git add
git commit

OR

git commit -a

Be careful to review only files you need are being comitted

6. In case you need to ammed your last commit based on review comments
git commit --amend

7. Push changes for review
git push origin HEAD:refs/for/master

8. Go through browser interface and submit once approved (+2)
http://gerrit-lvn-07.lvn.broadcom.net:8085/#/dashboard/self

9. Once you are done remove the local branch
git branch -D <branchname>

10. Rebase. Use with care

git checkout master
git pull

git checkout <branchname>
git rebase -i master

git diff -b master
git diff -b origin/master

11. In case you run into problems

git checkout master
git pull

git checkout -D <old branch>

Goto browser, Click on Download, Copy the Checkout line to clipboard
Paste line in shell, will show head in detached state

git checkout -b <old branch>

git rebase -i master

git diff -b master
git diff -b origin/master

Make your changes
git commit -a --amend

